{"hash":"8cdcb24eb6b965aabc424dc02a3705a76aba031a","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"e0460b2586e81605133fd739d7b305fe","title":"Ctlos Bspwm","description":"Описание конфигурации Ctlos Linux Bspwm, горячие клавиши, утилиты.","date":null,"date_up":"02.09.2020","path":"/wiki/wm/bspwm/","timeToRead":3,"content":"<h1 id=\"ctlos-linux-bspwm-031\"><a href=\"#ctlos-linux-bspwm-031\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Ctlos Linux Bspwm 0.3.1</h1>\n<p>Автор: Alex Creio <a href=\"https://t.me/cretm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">@cretm</a>.</p>\n<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1366 768' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-2aa819212e52ca24a41b30fbf1882540'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-2aa819212e52ca24a41b30fbf1882540)' width='1366' height='768' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAAkCAIAAAC2bqvFAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAQLElEQVRYw51Y%2bW9l1X2ff6FJwfZb776duy/n7tt79622n5%2bfl7E9g2e1ZzzAMIQkAwNBTENVNQQiQgW0LA0UpYpEW0IaidL2p0pESlt1idJUbdSfW7WVmv%2bg3/u8jD3DCIj10dH3nHvufedzvrtP7V57J02vKGhBk0cu3sTOmqlN/GDTNJYtcy2MtkBA4kCWhrI0L3IJz2CecY9DYD2GtFy8fOnyd/NsW5YiRU6RGAmsLwkhCKqSlosoVeVMRYlhFCLvc/Td37kHWGADQ%2bvA6/Ci4/SREBt6YRoFCApKsLN44fJLp4J413S2NGPdsLcsfNZ0zpj2mem4ZTtnHO%2bc6ZzVrU0DYJ%2bRpIRlZI7VOVY7DpZRRdE2zRZCLs/rPG/wnM4dQNufTsdSEHjjrtfvQrl5H7whCjbsFwRTFK2pYIFQfgceibaihKcUfVW3NjRrXUA9hmvzYhcgSD0O9Zt8m6JClkthyks9EQ1ZzqEogaKle0FSIkFwJDylRIoWp4viwdODFZGipGNP74smwZdoco0GWwKEOl2rkrUaVa9RtSpFkjzDII5TGw3mFFy8YW%2byQo4sv79x3skHuDXQ3SA3nW9MLmzceKu/9Yyddd0oM223QbB1gvuiqDWnb5F8neDrpNCYon58LNf5BsU3SNjGWtjzgiCI0zDJwiQNkiwbrQ42z/U3tgcb5/qnt3nVgaNznEySwilRSnnBAcaC4ecLK27WCzvzdpjZhrtaLLdWrwe9bS1oGX6m2CEl6l8UpKDxOjZczfSRHSiGK/KIZpEvqAEjYV6NaF5zfJ%2bgxN98gJiZox